hiveary-agent (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Complete rewrite of monitor loading, allowing arbitary monitors to be added.
  * Fixed several bugs related to automatic restarting.
  * Changed the format of alerts and how monitors are reported.
  * Improved the accuracy of the CPU resource monitor.
  * Send top processes by RAM or CPU with alerts for those resources.

